---
summary: Users should be able to "tag" rooms.
---
assignee: markjh
created: 2015-09-03 16:03:18.0
creator: markjh
description: |-
  Users should be able to set tags on rooms.

  These tags would only be visible to that user.

  These tags could be used to control where the room is displayed in the UI, For example rooms with a "favourite" tag could be moved to the top of the recents list.

  These tags could be used in notification rules. For example to only send notifications for channels with a "work" tag during working hours.

  These tags should appear in the room list displayed to the user.
