  body: 'for the use case of persisting room UI layout info in the server, I suspect we should also include a way of recording the positioning/ordering of rooms in the user''s recents list.  (i.e. this is favourite #1, this is favourite #2, this is the bottom most of my ''archive'' tags) etc.'
